Articles.Content:
So I just updated KSP to 1.1.1 via steam, copied it into separate directory and 

$ LC_ALL=C ./KSP.x86_64

as usual. Changed settings a little (resolution, volume, graphics) and started new sandbox. Loaded stock Bug-E, drifted a little, then decided to decouple this thing on top of it. And KSP just crashed. Right when I clicked this blue decouple button, a quarter second after releasing mouse button.
